title: Daz 3D - David
description:
David comes complete with all the enhanced features of a third generation Millennium figure. He uses new Pose Technology introduced with Victoria 3, with enhanced joint parameters and Joint Corrective Morph Targets. Texture maps are completely backwards compatible with Michael 3, and he has expanded material grouping, allowing him to be color mapped for tight-fitting clothing.
